title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race All Stars Season 7 - Episode 5
description:
Bob and Monét review Drag Race All Stars Season 7 Episode 5 "Draguation Speeches". The queens deliver inspiring and irreverent commencement speeches for draguates around the world. Nikki Glaser shares her comedic expertise and helps Mama Ru pick this week's Valedictorian.
See Monét and Bob on tour this fall by going to bobandmonet.com !!
